Package ides.api.model.fsa

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FSAModel
    Interface for models of Finite-State Automata.
    FSAPublisher
    A publisher of FSA messages.
    FSAState
    The interface defining a representation of a state in a finite state automaton.
    FSASubscriber
    Subscriber to messages sent by FSA models.
    FSASupervisor
    An FSA supervisor is an FSA with a control map.
    FSATransition
    Transition of an FSAModel.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FSAMessage
    Message sent to subscribers listening for changes to a FSA.
    FSAPublisherAdaptor
    Implementation of the FSAPublisher interface.
